description: Generated at the completion of Test Head completion.

event.Summary: OAM test head test completion status: $v16

objects.test: $SNMPTRAPCMD TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxOamTestHeadTestCompleted TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdName s EXAMPLE TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdOwner s EXAMPLE TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdStartTime s EXAMPLEE TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdCompletedTime s EXAMPLEE TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdElapsedTime i 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdProfIndex i 0 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdAccCritIndex i 1 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdPayLdIndex i 1 TIMETRA-SERV-MIB::svcId u 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdSapPortId u 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdSapEncapValue u 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdFc s EXAMPLE TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdDsiredThrpt i 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdCompleted i 1 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdStopped i 1 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdTestStatus i 1 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdAvgLatency i 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdFrLossRatio i 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdJitter i 9999 TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdAchvdThrpt i 9999

description: tmnxTestHdName is a mandatory parameter that needs to be
set along with tmnxTestHdAdminStatus to start a test head
test.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdName

description: tmnxTestHdOwner is a mandatory parameter that needs to be
set along with tmnxTestHdAdminStatus to start a test head
test.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdOwner

description: tmnxTestHdStartTime test head start time sent in the trap
message
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdStartTime

description: tmnxTestHdCompletedTime is the time at which test head run
has completed. tmnxTestHdCompletedTime is sent in the trap upon
test completion.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdCompletedTime

description: tmnxTestHdElapsedTime is the elapsed time since test head test
has started
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdElapsedTime

description: tmnxTestHdProfIndex profile index for this entry
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdProfIndex

description: tmnxTestHdPayLdIndex is the payload index
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdPayLdIndex

description: The value of the object svcId specifies the Service identifier. This
value should be unique within the service domain.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SERV-MIB::svcId

description: The Sap Port ID to be used for the test run, it has to be supplied
along with tmnxTestHdSapEncapValue when the test is started.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdSapPortId

description: The Sap Encap value to be used for the test run, it has to be supplied
along with tmnxTestHdSapPortId when the test is started.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdSapEncapValue

description: tmnxTestHdFc is an optional parameter that needs to be
set along with tmnxTestHdAdminStatus to start a test head
test.If tmnxTestHdFc is not given along with
tmnxTestHdAdminStatus default forwarding class 'be' would be
used
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdFc

description: tmnxTestHdDsiredThrpt is the desired through put in the test head
run. tmnxTestHdDsiredThrpt is sent in the trap upon test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdDsiredThrpt

description: tmnxTestHdCompleted is true if the test is completed else it is
false. tmnxTestHdCompleted is sent in the trap upon test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdCompleted

description: tmnxTestHdStopped is true if the test is stopped midway else it is
false. tmnxTestHdStopped is sent in the trap upon test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdStopped

description: tmnxTestHdTestStatus is sent in the trap upon test completion.
tmnxTestHdTestStatus is pass if the desired test results are
acheived.
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdTestStatus

description: tmnxTestHdAvgLatency is the measured average latency in the
test head run. tmnxTestHdAvgLatency is sent in the trap upon
test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdAvgLatency

description: tmnxTestHdFrLossRatio is the measured frame loss ratio
in the test head run. tmnxTestHdFrLossRatio is sent in the
trap upon test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdFrLossRatio

description: tmnxTestHdJitter is the measured jitter in the test head run.
tmnxTestHdJitter is sent in the trap upon test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdJitter

description: tmnxTestHdAchvdThrpt is the acheived through put in the test head
run. tmnxTestHdAchvdThrpt is sent in the trap upon test completion
variables.name: TIMETRA-SAS-OAM-TEST-MIB::tmnxTestHdAchvdThrpt
